    "comments": "Miguel Diaz - 02/20/23  9:09:57 AM:\u00a0Did maintenance below \n1)Check all safety devices.\n2)Inspect drive belts, replace if cracking.\n3)Top off cylinder oil if necessary.\n4)Tighten pulleys and pillow blocks.\n5)Lightly oil cylinder shafts.\n6)Check cutting surfaces and back plates for wear.\n7)Check saw blades for glue buildup and wear.\n8)Check oilers for drills and add oil when needed.\n9)Check for air leaks.\n10)Place a test piece in the machine and notch the door *Check to\n see that the door does not move forward or side to side adjust clamps if needed or replace drills \n11)Replaced both drill 49/64 and 3/8  drills.",
